Packages 
Package Description
com.mapdigit.drawing
The Drawing package provides access to basic 2D graphics functionality.
com.mapdigit.drawing.geometry
Provides the Java 2D classes for defining and performing operations on objects related to two-dimensional geometry.
com.mapdigit.gis
The gis package defines some common map objects.
com.mapdigit.gis.drawing
The Drawing package provides access to basic 2D graphics functionality.
com.mapdigit.gis.geometry
Provides the Java 2D classes for defining and performing operations on objects related to two-dimensional geometry.
com.mapdigit.gis.location
The gis package defines some common objects for location API.
com.mapdigit.gis.location.nmea
The gis package defines some common objects for NMEA compatiable location API.

The navigation package defines all classes used for navigation.

The packge defines raster digital map related classes.

The packge defines Digital map service interface.

Define vector map related classes.
